[
    {
        "content": "<p>How do I tell <code>x.py test</code>  to <em>skip</em> running tidy? It's pretty frustrating to have errors about extra newlines when I'm focused on testing if the code works first.</p>",
        "id": 215567827,
        "sender_full_name": "XAMPPRocky",
        "timestamp": 1604488685
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>--exclude src/tools/tidy</p>",
        "id": 215576904,
        "sender_full_name": "simulacrum",
        "timestamp": 1604495090
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>(or, in most cases, you want to restrict to just a couple test suites, e.g. ui for most compiler changes)</p>",
        "id": 215576960,
